This section gives a high-level overview of how the system works, its main functions, and the environment in which it operates.

Product Perspective

The Predictive Stock Management System is a standalone application designed to help businesses manage inventory and forecast demand. It improves traditional stock systems by adding prediction and analytics features.

Product Functions

Record stock-in and stock-out

Maintain inventory database

Analyze historical data

Predict future stock demand

Generate alerts for low stock

Display dashboards and reports

User Characteristics

Basic computer knowledge

No advanced technical skills required

Suitable for store managers and business owners

Constraints

Predictions depend on data quality

Limited to small and medium business use

Internet may be required for some features

This description provides a clear overview of what the system does and who it is for.
